-- German Confidence in Merkel’s Euro Policy Wanes, Bild Reports
-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 2012-07-29T13:17:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-29/german-confidence-in-merkel-s-euro-policy-wanes-bild-reports.html
Confidence in German Chancellor
 Angela Merkel ’s response to Europe’s sovereign debt crisis is
declining,  Bild  newspaper reported, citing YouGov Plc poll.  While 33 percent of those surveyed said Merkel is taking
“more or less” the right decisions, 48 percent said they don’t
agree with her policy, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
